                     <td width="100%" align="left" class="TableCell">I have had quite a break, I had some time off - bit of a burn out but I have been spending some hours putting together some
                        material for the Shards group. The biggest problem I have is the stats for NPCs - they just take <i>way</i> too long to lay out, so I will be putting together a simple app to get people to enter them into there and then I can auto-generate
                        the layout making that whole portion of it simple and easy and <b>standard</b>. 
                        
                        The first Shard in the list is making its way much closer to release now, I would expect it out within a couple of weeks -
                        FASA willing. 
                        
                        Bye for now!
                        Richard
